title: ICAM is the truth
content: Many asked Israel Cleon how is it that you have so much power in your name? I say, there's only one that has power in his name, thats jesus Christ after his father whom also has power. Therefore you can classify me as the Father as well as Jesus Christ with power and favor in my name. As you say Jesus Christ you are saying Cleon, Israel Cleon. Sign ICAM
